<emphasis id="B9219D51FFF5FA40DB6F3FA2FDF46AA2" bold="true" box="[557,578,1929,1955]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">C</emphasis>
. Female flower. 
<emphasis id="B9219D51FFF5FA40DA4F3FA2FC946AA2" bold="true" box="[781,802,1929,1955]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">D</emphasis>
. Habit showing blue iridescence. 
<emphasis id="B9219D51FFF5FA40DDFE3FA2FB666AA2" bold="true" box="[1212,1232,1929,1955]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">E</emphasis>
