; A, B, F from Bukit Sebelah, 
<emphasis id="B9219D51FFF5FA40D8A83FE4FC976AEB" box="[490,801,1999,2026]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Hughes &amp; Taufiq MH1541</emphasis>
. Scale bars on insets: B, C, E, F = 1 cm; D = 5 cm.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<subSubSection id="C34F12C8FFF4FA41D9FF3920FEE46C7D" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="8BEA4143FFF4FA41D9FF3920FEF26C24" blockId="7.[189,324,267,293]" box="[189,324,267,293]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">
<heading id="D0A2F62FFFF4FA41D9FF3920FEF26C24" bold="true" box="[189,324,267,293]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" reason="3">
<emphasis id="B9219D51FFF4FA41D9FF3920FEF26C24" bold="true" box="[189,324,267,293]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Etymology</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BEA4143FFF4FA41D9FF3917FEE46C7D" blockId="7.[189,1398,316,380]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">
The epithet is derived from the Indonesian word for “velvet”, 
<emphasis id="B9219D51FFF4FA41DADD3917FC4C6C57" box="[927,1018,316,342]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">beludru</emphasis>
, referring to the dense red hairs on the veins.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
